ADMIN_TOKEN=github_pat_<token>

------------------------------
Step-by-Step to generate it:

Open GitHub Settings:Go to your Fine-grained Personal Access Tokens page.

Edit the Token:Click on the name of the token you are using.

Repository Access:Look for the Repository access section near the top.Select Only select repositories.Click the Select repositories dropdown.Search for and check the box next to the specific repo you are trying to script.

Verify Administration:Scroll down to Permissions -> Repository permissions.Find Administration.Ensure it is still set to Read and Write.

Save:Click the Update token button at the bottom of the page.
--------------------------------